</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><htmlonly block="yes"> &lt;button class=&quot;collapsible&quot;&gt;</htmlonly> <bold>regularize_parallelism</bold> <htmlonly block="yes">&lt;/button&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;</htmlonly><itemizedlist>
